new-page: true

- @law_crime: Reduce the Crime Rate
- @law_police: Increase Number of Policemen
- @law_prison: Resolve Prison Overcrowding
- @law_reform: Reform the police
- @law_demilitarize: Demilitarize the police
- @law_system: Reform the prison system
